Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord0\fad(1500,500)\pos(190,175)}好夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord0\fad(1500,500)}编剧：史蒂文·莫法特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,River 到安特卫普再见\N{\fs14}River! I'll see you in Antwerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉玛丽莲她太迟了\N{\fs14}Tell Marilyn she's too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,必须坐双翼飞机过来了\N{\fs14}she'll have to use the biplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,保重\N{\fs14}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你每天晚上都这么做吗\N{\fs14}Do you do this every night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你正尝试藏起一个中音号\N{\fs14}You're trying to conceal a euphonium.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一副有罪的样子 你以前就经常这么干么\N{\fs14}Guiltily. Has that ever been attempted before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 这个啊 没错\N{\fs14}What? Oh, this. Oh, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它就是一个普通的中音号\N{\fs14}it's just one of those euphoniums.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 所以我们晚上睡觉的时候 你就在干这个\N{\fs14}Okay, so is this what you do at night when we're sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去经历更多的冒险\N{\fs14}Have extra adventures?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有你们睡得时间长 我得找点事情做\N{\fs14}I don't sleep as much as you. I keep busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,忙着做些什么 这一次就告诉我吧\N{\fs14}Doing what? Actually, tell me for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:00:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友\N{\fs14}You're my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友\N{\fs14}my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你究竟都做些什么吧\N{\fs14}So tell me what it is you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我刚帮助了月球基地里一个被附身的管弦乐队\N{\fs14}Okay. I just helped out a possessed orchestra on a moon base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在此之前 我阻止了两颗超新星爆发\N{\fs14}Before that, I prevented two supernovas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,重写了宇宙的历史 都是开玩笑的\N{\fs14}wrote a history of the universe, all in jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还在布里克斯顿做了点临时代理的工作\N{\fs14}and did a bit of locum work in Brixton.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的业务 十分缺人手\N{\fs14}Lovely practice, very short-staffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是你生命中微不足道的一小部分 不是吗\N{\fs14}We're all such tiny parts of your life, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友们都来了又走 匆匆而过\N{\fs14}All the friends you make just flicker in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定都注意不到我们\N{\fs14}You must hardly notice us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy\N{\fs14}AMY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是我生命中很重要的部分\N{\fs14}you are enormous parts of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我唯一能留下的回忆\N{\fs14}And you are all I ever remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,说起这个\N{\fs14}Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生不合常理\N{\fs14}My life doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我一直想和你谈的\N{\fs14}That's what I've been trying to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,比如\N{\fs14}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当我第一次遇见你时 我没有父母\N{\fs14}when I first met you, I didn't have parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有过父母\N{\fs14}I never had parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在你做了所有那些事之后\N{\fs14}And then you did whatever it was you did
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你重启了宇宙 突然间…\N{\fs14}and rebooted the universe and suddenly, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我有父母了\N{\fs14}had parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我一直都有父母\N{\fs14}And I've always had parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,两种人生都在我的记忆里\N{\fs14}And I remember both lives in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,两种记忆同时存在\N{\fs14}both of them in my head at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样挺好的不是吗\N{\fs14}And it's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不应该是这样的\N{\fs14}Yeah, but it shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会挺好的呢\N{\fs14}Why is it fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rory 做了2000年的罗马人\N{\fs14}Rory was a Roman for 2000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他几乎不记得了\N{\fs14}He says he hardly remembers it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 有时你会发现他发呆凝望\N{\fs14}Ah, but sometimes you catch him just staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy 关键是\N{\fs14}The thing is, Amy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人的记忆都是一团乱麻\N{\fs14}everyone's memory is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,生活本身就是一团乱麻\N{\fs14}Life is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,每人都会有那些记忆\N{\fs14}Everyone's got memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,比如一场他们没有度过的假\N{\fs14}of a holiday they couldn't have been on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或是他们从未参加的宴会\N{\fs14}or a party they never went to,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,或者与某人初次相遇\N{\fs14}or met someone for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,却感到认识他们一辈子了\N{\fs14}and felt like they've known them all their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,时间正在被重写 就在我们周围 就在每一天\N{\fs14}Time is being rewritten all around us, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人们觉得是自己的记忆不好\N{\fs14}People think their memories are bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他们的记忆没问题\N{\fs14}but their memories are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,过去真的就是这个样子的\N{\fs14}The past is really like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这太荒谬了\N{\fs14}That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你现在开始明白了\N{\fs14}Yeah, now you're starting to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放在那里\N{\fs14}Put your hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,塔迪斯心灵感应电路\N{\fs14}Tardis telepathic circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做什么\N{\fs14}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不用做 只要放松\N{\fs14}Nothing, just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你最悲伤的记忆是在一个露天马戏场 1994年\N{\fs14}Your saddest ever memory was at a fairground in 1994.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得是为什么吗\N{\fs14}Can you remember why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不记得 等等 是不是…\N{\fs14}No. Hang on, did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我冰激凌掉地上了\N{\fs14}Did I drop an ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能是我最悲伤的回忆\N{\fs14}That can't be my saddest memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,冰激凌的记忆总是悲伤的\N{\fs14}Remembering ice cream's always sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们着陆了么 我们在哪儿\N{\fs14}Did we just land? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你冰激凌掉地上以后发生了什么\N{\fs14}What happened after you dropped the ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有 我一直在哭\N{\fs14}Nothing, I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 等下 有一位女士\N{\fs14}No, no, hang on. There was a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她又给我买了一个\N{\fs14}And she bought me another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她真好 她长什么样子\N{\fs14}Good for her. What did she look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起来…\N{\fs14}She looked like she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿着滑稽的衣服 一件睡衣\N{\fs14}She had a funny dress, a nightdress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她长着红头发\N{\fs14}She had red hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs14}Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做 有什么意义呢\N{\fs14}Why are you doing this? What is the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那位好心的女士她对你说了什么\N{\fs14}The nice lady, what did she say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,开心点 享受你的冰激凌吧\N{\fs14}Cheer up. Have an ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy 时间与空间从来都不符合什么常理\N{\fs14}Amy, time and space is never ever going to make any kind of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前 你就得到了关于\N{\fs14}A long time ago, you got
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如何对待它的最好的建议\N{\fs14}the best possible advice on how to deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我建议\N{\fs14}So, I suggest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你去给出这个建议\N{\fs14}So, I suggest you go and give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 我\N{\fs14}Okay, okay, so I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,问了你一个关于人生的重大问题\N{\fs14}ask a big, important question about life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而你基本上就是告诉我\N{\fs14}and you're basically telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去给自己买个冰激凌\N{\fs14}to go and buy myself an ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不 Amy 我在告诉你\N{\fs14}No, Amy, I am telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,去给我们俩一人买一个\N{\fs14}to go and buy us both ice creams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我超爱露天马戏场\N{\fs14}I love fairgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌你\N{\fs14}I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不会呢\N{\fs14}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你坐幽灵列车的时候会害怕么 我有点怕\N{\fs14}Do you get scared on ghost trains? I get a bit scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我能不能抓着你的手呢\N{\fs14}So is it okay if I hold your hand?
